:: Cultural

:: School

:: Daylight Saving

:: Seasons

: Spring
"الربيع"                 on march 20
: Summer
"الصيف"                       on june 21
: Fall
"الخريف"                   on september 23
: Winter
"الشتاء"                     on december 21

